| OS                 | Zorin OS 17.2                                              |
| Kernel             | 6.8.0-52-generic                                           |
| Uptime             | up 8 hours, 8 minutes                                      |
+--------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+
| CPU Model          | AMD Ryzen 5 3500X 6-Core Processor                         |
| CPU Cores          | 6                                                          |
+--------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+
| Total RAM          | 31Gi                                                       |
| Used RAM           | 11Gi                                                       |
| Free RAM           | 12Gi                                                       |
