+--------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+

Detailed Hardware Information:
To view detailed hardware information, run: sudo lshw -short
Script executed successfully.
            </pre>
        </div>
    </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
    .about-container {
        max-width: 800px;
    }

    .prompt {
        color: var(--ctp-green);
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .about-section {
        margin: 2rem 0;
        padding-bottom: 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--ctp-overlay0);
    }

    .about-section:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }

    .terminal-output {
        background-color: var(--ctp-crust);
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 1rem;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }

    .terminal-output pre {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--ctp-text);
        white-space: pre-wrap;
    }

    .experience-block {
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .experience-block h3 {
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        color: var(--ctp-blue);
    }

    .meta {
        color: var(--ctp-subtext0);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .interests-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .interest-tag {
        background-color: var(--ctp-surface1);
        color: var(--ctp-lavender);
        padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
</style>